let masopeningLines = [`a name that rolls off the tongue, A man so charming, he could never be outdone.`, `His smile is like the sun, warm and bright, It fills my heart with such delight.`, `The way he moves is poetry in motion, He's a work of art, a true devotion.`, `His eyes are like stars in the midnight sky, I can't help but get lost, I can't deny.`, `His laugh is music to my ears, A symphony that erases all my fears.`, `I could spend eternity in his embrace, Forever lost in his warm, loving grace.`, `A man like him is truly one of a kind, And I am lucky to have him on my mind.`,
	`Tall and broad-shouldered, with a chiseled jaw,`, `His eyes, like deep pools, draw me in,`, `There's a certain strength in the way he moves,`, `With a rugged exterior and a tender heart,`, `His smile is a ray of sunshine on a cloudy day,`, `His laughter echoes through the room,`, `He's a man of few words, but when he speaks,`, `His hands, rough and calloused, tell the story of hard work,`, `There's a kindness in his eyes that's hard to miss,`, `He carries himself with an air of quiet confidence,`,
	`In his presence, I am both comforted and intimidated.`, `His aura is magnetic, drawing me in without any effort.`, `He exudes a sense of power and control that is hard to ignore.`, `I can't help but be captivated by his piercing gaze.`, `He moves with a grace that belies his strength.`, `There's a hint of mischief in his smile that makes my heart race.`, `His voice is a deep rumble that resonates within me.`, `I'm struck by the intensity of his focus, as if nothing else exists in the world.`,
	`He wears his scars like badges of honor, proof of the battles he's fought.`, `There's a quiet intensity to him that is both alluring and intimidating.`, `He walks into the room and all eyes are on him, drawn like moths to a flame.`, `There's a raw sensuality in the way he moves, like he's always ready for a fight or a dance.`, `With a presence that commands attention, he strides through life like a king in his realm.`, `He wears his heart on his sleeve, but his emotions are a stormy sea that he keeps carefully contained.`, `He has a voice like honey and a gaze like steel, drawing me in and keeping me there.`, `He's a man of contrasts, rough and smooth, dark and light, with a complexity that I can't resist.`, `His scent is like a drug, heady and intoxicating, making me feel both alive and vulnerable.`, `He's a mystery wrapped in an enigma, a puzzle that I want to solve but can never quite figure out.`, `He's like a wild animal, all primal energy and fierce determination, with a danger that's both thrilling and terrifying.`, `His laughter is infectious, like a contagion that spreads joy and happiness wherever he goes.`, `He's a man of action, not words, but his actions speak volumes about his character and his heart.`,
	`He has a smile that lights up the world, like a sunburst that warms my soul and brightens my day.`, `He's a paradox, a tough exterior hiding a gentle soul, a fighter who yearns for peace, a man who defies easy categorization.`, `He's like a force of nature, unstoppable and untamed, with a power that both fascinates and scares me.`, `He's a man who knows what he wants and goes after it with single-minded determination, never wavering or faltering in his quest.`, `With a brooding intensity that matches the storm clouds gathering on the horizon, he fills me with a sense of foreboding and excitement.`,
	`He's a man who's seen the dark side of life and come out the other side stronger and wiser, with a depth of experience that's both humbling and inspiring.`, `There's a vulnerability in his eyes that he tries to hide, but I can see it there, a glimpse of the real man beneath the tough exterior.`, `He's a rebel and a maverick, a man who defies convention and rules, carving his own path through life with a fierce independence.`, `His shoulders bear the weight of the world, but his spirit is unbreakable.`, `There's a restlessness in his soul that keeps him searching for something more.`,
	`He moves with a fluid grace, like a dancer in tune with the music of life.`, `His eyes are the color of the ocean, deep and full of mysteries waiting to be explored.`, `There's a quiet intensity to him that draws me in like a moth to a flame.`, `He's a man of few words, but each one carries the weight of the world.`,
	`His voice is like a song, soothing and enchanting, wrapping me in a warm embrace.`, `There's a sense of danger that surrounds him, like a storm cloud waiting to unleash its fury.`, `He's a warrior at heart, fierce and unrelenting in his pursuit of what he believes in.`, `His smile is like a ray of sunshine, warming my soul and lighting up my day.`, `There's a wisdom in his eyes that belies his youth, like an old soul that's lived a hundred lifetimes.`,
	`With a gaze that pierces through my soul, he leaves me breathless.`, `His rugged exterior is a mask for the tenderness within, a contradiction that fascinates me.`, `He's a man who stands tall, proud and unyielding, like a monument to strength and resilience.`, `His hands are skilled and precise, creating works of art that take my breath away.`, `He's a man of quiet contemplation, lost in thought but always aware of his surroundings.`, `There's a fire in his eyes that burns with a passion for life and all its possibilities.`, `He's a man who lives life on his own terms, refusing to be held back by anyone or anything.`,
	`His laughter is like music, a symphony of joy and happiness that lifts my spirits.`, `He moves with a confident ease, like a panther stalking its prey, always in control.`, `There's a grace in his movements that speaks of discipline and dedication, a testament to his character.`,
	`He's a man who wears his scars with pride, each one a reminder of battles fought and won.`, `His presence fills the room, commanding attention and respect without saying a word.`, `He's a man of contradictions, strong and vulnerable, fierce and gentle, a puzzle I can't resist.`, `His eyes hold secrets that he guards closely, a mystery waiting to be unraveled.`, `He's a force to be reckoned with, unstoppable and unrelenting, a true champion.`,
	`His smile is infectious, spreading joy and happiness wherever he goes.`, `There's a vulnerability in his voice that touches my heart, a glimpse of the man behind the mask.`, `He's a man of action, always moving forward, always striving for something more.`, `His touch is electric, igniting a fire within me that I can't ignore.`];

let masclosingLines = [`And in his heart, a fire burns bright.`, `He stands tall, unbroken, unbowed.`, `A man of honor, grace, and might.`, `And so he walks, his head held high.`,
	`For he is more than flesh and bone.`, `He is a beacon in the night.`, `And though the road be long and hard,`, `He never falters, never falls.`, `For he is steadfast, true, and strong.`, `And thus he triumphs over all.`,
	`And as he moves forward, the world moves with him.`, `In his eyes, a quiet determination burns.`, `He wears his scars like badges of honor.`, `With every step, he leaves a trail of greatness behind.`,
	`For he knows that even in the darkness, he carries his own light.`, `His strength lies not in his muscle, but in his mind.`, `And so he stands, a titan among men.`, `For he knows that true victory is won within.`, `He is a warrior, but also a poet of life.`, `And thus he lives, a testament to resilience and hope.`,
	`With each breath, he proves that he is alive.`, `For he is a man of courage, compassion, and drive.`, `He walks with purpose, guided by his own light.`, `And so he endures, even in the darkest of nights.`,
	`With every word and deed, he inspires and uplifts.`, `For he knows that in giving, one truly receives.`, `He embraces the challenges that come his way.`, `And with each obstacle, he becomes stronger each day.`,
	`For he believes that every setback is an opportunity to learn.`, `And so he forges ahead, with passion and concern.`, `He sees the beauty in the world, even amidst its strife.`,
	`And with an unwavering spirit, he brings color to life.`, `For he knows that in this journey, he is never alone.`, `And with each other, we build a brighter tomorrow.`, `He may stumble, but he always rises once more.`,
	`For he understands that failure is just another door.`, `With his heart on his sleeve, he faces the unknown.`, `And with each passing moment, he has grown.`, `He may not know where the road will lead.`, `But he trusts in his strength and his own creed.`, `With his eyes on the prize, he marches on.`,
	`For he knows that his struggles will soon be gone.`, `His heart beats with a steady, resolute beat.`, `And he refuses to accept defeat.`, `For he is a fighter, a true champion at heart.`,
	`And he will never let his spirit fall apart.`, `He stands firm in his values and his beliefs.`, `And in his wake, he leaves only relief.`, `For he is a man of his word and his will.`,
	`And he will always strive for what is good and still.`, `He is a force to be reckoned with, a true gem.`, `And with each passing day, he becomes more of them.`,
	`For he knows that every journey begins with a single step.`, `And with each step, he grows stronger, filled with pep.`, `He is a man of his own making, a true pioneer.`,
	`And with each new challenge, he becomes more sincere.`, `For he is a beacon of light in a world so dark.`, `And with his presence, he leaves a lasting mark.`, `He knows that there is always hope, always a way.`, `And with his actions, he makes each and every day count, every single day.`];

